data.description: Home on acreage with detached 42x42 garage/workshop with new garage door and opener. Home features 2 Story Entry with exposed staircase. Living room with Vault Ceiling & Stacked stone fireplace flanked by built in bookcases. Open Kitchen/Dining with quartz counter tops with Refinished Hardwood Flooring, center island, plus a pantry. Remodeled Main level Master bedroom steps out to a large back deck with trex boards  with scenic view. Both remodeled guest bedrooms have walk in closets and share an adjoining all tile bath from floor to ceiling . The main level has a drive thru 2 bay garage with 4 new garage doors annd openers and the basement is unfinished but has been insulated and have all new shower toilet and vanity that will convey for future expansion with a 1 bay garage with new garage door opener. Detached garage is on separate meter and septic. Great storage for RV, Boat, Tractor, Hobby cars, atvs and side by sides or awesome workshop. All on level 3.3 acres. Don’t miss your opportunity to own a awesome home next to wind rock mountain and 10mins to oak ridge!
data.whatILove: Minutes from windrock, Oak Ridge and Knoxville!!
